Summary
Some key things to take from this topic:

Data Science is about data:

Data collection;
Data management;
Data storage;
Data structure;
Data analysis;
Data, Data, Data ...

Data Science is also about…

Collaboration!

The schedule is tentative;
Jupiter Notebook will be the main tool of the course, but there are other IDEs:

Google Colab
Quarto

Hands on! First Commit




To check all commits in your repo:



git log



Most important things here are:

commit id;
date/time;
branch;
commit message;
